genresAdvancedInfo.name: sulawesi indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Sulawesi indie is a relatively new genre of music that emerged from the Indonesian island of Sulawesi. It is characterized by its eclectic mix of traditional and modern sounds, incorporating elements of rock, pop, and traditional Sulawesi music. Sulawesi indie artists often sing in the local language and address social issues and cultural identity in their lyrics. The genre has gained popularity in recent years, especially among young people in Sulawesi
